      "comment": "MOCAMBORA MIA (1) had the drop on the lead early on but could only manage second, beaten 1.3 lengths (17.97) at this track in a Other over 305m. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Top chance in this line up. ROUGH GIRL MEL (5) produced a moderate effort last time when fifth at this track over 305m behind Jazzy Boo (18.39) in a Other. Placed at her previous run. Key player if finds best. TESTED (8) was well fancied last time and led throughout to score (18.05) at this track in a Other over 305m. Deserves serious consideration again. SHE'S DRIVEN (2) is worth some thought after a surprise placing last start.",
